\[\mathrm{Reg}_{\mu}^{(T)},\mathrm{Reg}_{i}^{(T)}=O\left(\frac{1}{\eta}+\eta \left(1+\mathcal{V}_{CE}^{(T)}+\mathcal{V}_{\mathbf{A}}^{(T)}\right)\right),\]

